<XSLTdocConfig>
  <Title>Krextor RDF Extractor</Title>
  <Introduction>
    <p>
	Krextor is an extensible XSLT-based framework for extracting RDF from
	XML, supporting multiple input languages as well as multiple output RDF
	notations. Krextor provides convenience templates that try to do “the
	right thing”™ in many common cases, as to reduce the need for manually
	writing repetitive code.
    </p>
    <p>
	<a href="http://kwarc.info/projects/krextor/">Project Page</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
	Please report bugs by using the <a href="https://trac.kwarc.info/krextor/">bug tracking tool</a>.
      <br />Any comments are welcome.
    </p>
  </Introduction>
